# View migration logs

Learn how to access and interpret migration logs, including details such as start time, end time, progress, and status.

You can view the migration process and result in the migration log. You can also view migration logs for any historical migration.

To view the migration logs, navigate to the Migration Logs section.

![MigrationLogs.png](https://zuora.deploy.heretto.com/v4/deployments/QPAZk6lsgXwvotedNERE/object/60a24abe-1c28-4295-ab1c-04693a8dca35?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..ZyhReIdHvOBUINAMekpXqyi-ZKFcv0mwFHrMUbFc7PM)

As the preceding diagram shows, you can see the following information for a migration:

-   Start Time

-   End Time

-   Generated By

-   Cutover Date

-   Progress

-   Status: see the following table for all the possible statuses for a migration.

    | Status | Description |
    | --- | --- |
    | Accepted | The migration request is accepted. |
    | In progress | The data migration is in progress. |
    | Error | Some errors occur, and migration is not successful. Contact Zuora Global Support for more information |
    | Completed | The data migration is completed, and all the data is generated successfully. |
    | Completed-Warning | The data migration is completed. However, the data is partially generated, and some cannot be generated. Contact Zuora Global Support for more information. |


You can also click the Action icon ![ActionIcon.png](https://zuora.deploy.heretto.com/v4/deployments/QPAZk6lsgXwvotedNERE/object/183b5ec4-8d4a-4699-98e9-ff73a7cf6f7f?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..wJ_deImlrpywV3ACwZRKmD0HbNAYjCZ0VY4cPnJtBv8) to open the Migration log details window and view more detailed information, as in the following diagram.

![MigrationLogDetails.png](https://zuora.deploy.heretto.com/v4/deployments/QPAZk6lsgXwvotedNERE/object/ae286ab1-5c79-4053-b48f-4cdadcfa3b5c?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..tK-QCl235PjneYxyZb3_AdgEE_QXm878Ca15hlVhSI0)
